hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Yes, I play the guitar medbox24.com It surprised me how easy it was simply to ask questions of people in public places. I would simply find out where my target consumers would be and ask them loads of questions until they’d had enough. I may have gone too far though: on one occasion, a gym owner accused me of harassing his customers and the police were called. Luckily, the police concluded that I wasn’t obstructing anyone and allowed me to continue merrily asking my questions.
